2005-08-14 23:04  pgregory

	* render/: kdtree.h, points.cpp, points.h: Fix problem with
	  RiPoints primitives, introduced during refactor of the KDTree
	  implementation for the new sampling code. As the KDTree didn't
	  end up getting used in the new sampling code, I reverted to the
	  old implementation.

2005-08-13 10:13  pgregory

	* render/subdivision2.cpp: More fixes to the subdivision surface
	  code to improve the handling of varying and facevarying primitive
	  variables. Now efforts are made to ensure that quads resulting
	  from subdivision match the parent polygon's orientation, thus
	  making grid points match up better.

2005-08-09 13:25  pgregory

	* SConstruct, aqsis/SConscript, aqsl/SConscript,
	  aqsltell/SConscript, display/SConscript,
	  libaqsistypes/SConscript, libargparse/SConscript,
	  libcodegenvm/SConscript, libddmanager/SConscript,
	  libraytrace/SConscript, libri2rib/SConscript, librib2/SConscript,
