	* libslparse/: parsenode.h, parser.yxx, typecheck.cpp: More changes
	  to the function call typechecking in slparse, now more robust.

2005-08-04 21:21  pgregory

	* ChangeLog: Update for release.

2005-08-02 04:37  tshead

	* libslparse/typecheck.cpp: * Fix: compile problem with
	  const-correctness

2005-08-01 12:44  pgregory

	* libslparse/typecheck.cpp: Fix error when weighting function
	  candidates by return type when typechecking overloaded function
	  calls.

2005-08-01 10:08  pgregory

	* libshaderexecenv/shadeops.cpp, libshaderexecenv/shaderexecenv.h,
	  libshadervm/shadervm.cpp, libshadervm/shadervm.h,
	  libshadervm/shadervm2.cpp, libslparse/parsenode.cpp,
	  libslparse/parsenode.h, libslparse/typecheck.cpp,
	  render/ishaderexecenv.h: Redo the function call typechecking
	  code. Now chooses the best (hopefully) function from the list (of
	  functions with the same name) by weighting them according to the
	  suitability, taking into account arguments passed in, and return
	  value.

2005-07-28 22:14  pgregory

	* ChangeLog: Update changelog for release.

