	* libaqsistypes/Makefile.am, render/Makefile.am: Fix the inclusion
	  of MultiTimer.h/cpp.

2005-07-26 21:32  pgregory

	* render/curves.cpp: Fix bug #1102605. The curve wasn't being
	  rendered properly becuase it wasn't calculating the tangent
	  vectors at the endpoints properly due to coincident points. The
	  fix may not be ideal, but seems to work for the moment, may need
	  revisiting.

