	* teqser/Makefile.am, aqsis/Makefile.am:

	  make sure both teqser and aqsis pulls into the list of libraries
	  fltk, and in context of MacosX the framework.

2005-03-28 00:47  joron

	* librib2/scanner.lxx, libslparse/scanner.lxx:

	  We will assume the MACOSX is identical in term of tools like
	  flex/bison as the port for Linux.  So the parser.h will be used
	  instead of parser.h.cpp (as on NT) or previously known as
	  parser.hpp.

	  for both renderer/librib2, renderer/libslparse.

