2004-08-07 17:41  tshead

	* Makefile.am, configure.ac, aqsis/Makefile.am, aqsis/aqsis.cpp,
	  aqsltell/Makefile.am, aqsltell/aqsltell.cpp, bin/Makefile.am,
	  bin/displays.ini, display/Makefile.am, display/displays.ini,
