	  typo in configure.ac

2004-06-07 23:00  pgregory

	* configure.ac, libshaderexecenv/shadeops.cpp,
	  libshaderexecenv/shaderexecenv.h, render/curves.cpp,
	  render/ilightsource.h, render/ishaderexecenv.h,
	  render/isurface.h, render/lights.h, render/micropolygon.cpp: Add
	  Boost threads and functions sections to the included Boost
	  source.  Fix bug #967456. The surface() function was getting the
	  surface shader from the current state at the point the
	  lightsource was instantiated. Instead it should get the surface
	  being lit.

